{"tid":563828,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葉念琛：Stephy拍我先掂","createTime":"2018-02-17T10:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T10:34:38.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df890089bca573bf0b7f23f05cb7e49c3fe46ad8","tid":563828,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"王菀之（Ivana）跟葉念琛合作賀歲片《我的情敵女婿》，早前他們在觀塘接受訪問，講到導演的外號，Ivana一口就能說出：「『MK活地阿倫』，佢喺片場成日講，道具海報都寫住呢個名，佢好proud of呢個稱號。」<br />\n在葉念琛電影中，「阿寶」是必然角色，今次由劉嘉玲擔演。去年鄧麗欣（Stephy）大豐收，憑《空手道》奪電影評論學會最佳女演員，有網民就拿葉念琛來比較，葉念琛說：「睇你揀乜箒！佢拍我嘅戲先係最賣座最受歡迎。」更笑言Stephy部份近作都不及自己一部的票房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d5ebc6b3ff7659f767bfece1bd3c29b529e354","tid":563828,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180217/20307646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180217%2F20307646&d=v1VleAHhEtVq%2BT6ZJOMX9QEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=c6f44f86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180217%2F20307646&h=355ef1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180217/20307646</a>"},{"pid":"dec1eac143e0d5ab1ddd7df637e2af7b870be88d","tid":563828,"uid":43231,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"香港地<br />\n無恥可以做特首<br />\n傻仔都可以做導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a037b7aa9d4b3c1ba5b78d083313a6c6b2559500","tid":563828,"uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"雖然佢捧stephy係有番咁上下，但係淨係靠佢呢啲千篇一律嘅作品，如果鬥心冇乜嘅話，都唔會有今日，至少只係靠佢嘅話，stephy未必會有機會接到《空手道》、《藍天白雲》呢啲相對有深度嘅作品。<br />\n睇下之前同stephy 合作嘅方力申，咁耐以來都係冇乜出色表現<img sr